.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: corn, pineapple, potato
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, photographer, pilot
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, singing, puzzles
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating corn##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the pilot and the person eating potato##2
3. the photographer is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person eating potato is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3       |
| Food    | corn   | pineapple | potato       |
| Job     | pilot  | musician  | photographer |
| Hobby   | singing | fishing  | puzzles       |

