.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-9::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, snowmobile, tram
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, polish, thai
3 different pets are kept: goat, rabbit, rat
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the pakistani is in an odd position##4
3. the polish is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
4. the pakistani is on the right of the polish##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the owner of the goat and the person driving the snowmobile##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |       3       |
| Transport         | snowmobile | roller | tram |
| Nationality   | thai       | polish  | pakistani     |
| Pet           | rabbit     | rat     | goat          |

