.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, nurse, photographer
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, july, june
There are 3 different nationalities: german, russian, thai
1. the nurse is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the german is on the left or right of the thai##3
4. the chef is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the thai is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3    |
| Job           | photographer | chef        | nurse   |
| Birthday   | july | june | september    |
| Nationality   | thai         | german      | russian |

