4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | fanta  | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | country  | pop    | disco       |
| Job   | electrician   | designer | musician   |

